<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.10.11">
<l>āṭceyta tāḻippi rāṉaic cērntavaṉ vaṇkuru kūrnakarā</l>
<l>ṉāṭka maḻmakiḻ mālai mārpiṉaṉ māṟaṉ caṭakōpaṉ</l>
<l>vēṭkai yālcoṉṉa pāṭal āyirat tuḷippat tumvallār</l>
<l>mīṭci yiṉṟi vaikunta mānakar maṟṟatu kaiyatuvē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master this decade among the thousand of songs spoken out of desire</l>
<l>by Māṟaṉ Caṭakōpaṉ, a garland with nectar fragrant of the day on his chest,</l>
<l>the one from the city of liberal Kurukūr, who has joined the lord of the discus in service,</l>
<l>it has in hand nothing else but the great city of Vaikuntam, without return.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
